1.css tag/element selector:

selector{
    property: value;
}

e.g
h1{
    color: red;
    font-size: 32px;
}


2.class selector:
<section>
    <button class="btn">
        Subscribe Thapa Technical
    </button>
</section>

<!-- we use class to stylize that specific tag -->
 .btn{
    color: blue;
    font-weight: bold;
 }

 3.ID selector
 #btn{
    color: blue;
    font-weight: bold;
 }


 pseudo-class
 a:hover{
    color: blue;
    font-weight: bold;
 }

 